title: Saint Laurent Paris Baby Downtown Cabas
description: Saint Laurent Paris baby downtown cabas handbag in beige grained calfskin leather. Featuring dual leather top handles, aged gold-toned hardware, and a detachable flat leather shoulder strap. The fold over strap with YSL logo magnetic button and zipper closures open to a black textile-lined interior with a leather patch pocket. Approx dimensions: 25.5cm(W) x 17.5cm(H) x 13cm(D), 9.5cm handle drop and 49.5cm shoulder strap drop. Accompanied by a YSL dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticit
